{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/add-background-image-to-debut-footer","result":{"pageContext":{"id":443,"date":"2021-02-20T07:15:42","date_gmt":"2021-02-20T07:15:42","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=443"},"modified":"2022-05-07T09:50:17","modified_gmt":"2022-05-07T09:50:17","slug":"add-background-image-to-debut-footer","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/add-background-image-to-debut-footer/","title":{"rendered":"Add a background image to Debut&#8217;s footer"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Design limitations are, unfortunately, a reality for most of the themes out there. Depending on the type of design your business has, a background image may work better than just a simple color. <br><br>In this post we will teach you how you can quickly add an image to your Debut theme footer.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-locating-the-file-to-add-the-code\">Locating the file to add the code</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>In your Shopify admin, go to&nbsp;<strong>Online Store</strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Themes&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Actions&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Edit Code</strong>.</li><li>Find the&nbsp;<strong>theme.css</strong>&nbsp;file in your theme. Keep in mind that depending on your theme’s version this file can also be named&nbsp;<strong>theme.scss.liquid</strong> or <strong>theme.scss</strong></li><li>Add the following code:</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-syntaxhighlighter-code\">.site-footer {\nbackground-image: url(https://www.toptal.com/designers/subtlepatterns/patterns/double-bubble-outline.png);\nbackground-color: unset;\nposition: relative;\n}</pre>\n\n\n\n<p>Please bear in mind that you need to change the link between parenthesis in the code above with the URL of the image you want to use. <br><br><a href=\"http://ezfycode.com/blog/how-to-upload-images-and-files-to-your-shopify-store\">Click here</a> to learn how to upload your own image to Shopify &amp; generate an URL to use it with the code above.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"you-may-also-like\">You may also like</h3>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"custom-you-may-also-like\">Here are some other tutorials you may be interested in:<br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/debut-shopify-theme-how-to-add-swipe-for-product-page-images\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&#8211; Add arrows &amp; swiping to Debut product pages<span><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media3.giphy.com/media/3EkLfaQZ4YQKaZ26OY/giphy.gif\"></span></a><br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/debut-theme-product-page-images-zoom-tutorial\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&#8211; Debut &#8220;click to zoom&#8221; lightbox tutorial: mobile friendly images, slider &amp; arrows<span><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media1.giphy.com/media/WR5Yl3hW8x6aUilwRe/giphy.gif\"></span></a><br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/how-to-disable-right-click-image-and-text-copying-without-apps\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&#8211; Improve your website&#8217;s safety: block right click, image copying and more</a></p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Use a background image in your Debut theme instead of an unique color.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":448,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[157],"acf":[],"image_alt":"","featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Debut-Slider-Pro-3-1-600x338.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Debut-Slider-Pro-3-1-100x100.png","featured_image_large_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Debut-Slider-Pro-3-1-1200x675.png","categories_names":["Blog"],"tag_names":["debut theme"],"featured_image_url":"https://www.e